data.oai_dc:dc: Digestion time of Oculina arbuscula fed Artemia sp. based on the prey DNA content estimated by qPCR

Concentration of Artemia sp. prey DNA ingested by Oculina arbuscula after 0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 6, 8 and 10 days. Prey DNA concentration is shown for different amplicon sizes amplified with different primer sets.
